<subSubSection pageId="55" pageNumber="56" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="55.[189,1399,1487,1989]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<bibRefCitation author="Almada F. &amp; Henriques M. &amp; Levy A. &amp; Pereira A. &amp; Robalo J. &amp; Almada V. C." box="[242,472,1735,1759]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" pagination="1151 - 1156" refId="ref38099" refString="Almada F., Henriques M., Levy A., Pereira A., Robalo J. &amp; Almada V. C. 2008. Reclassification of Lepadogaster candollei based on molecular and meristic evidence with a redefinition of the genus Lepadogaster. Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 46: 1151 - 1156. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1016 / j. ympev. 2007.05.021" type="journal article" year="2008">
Almada 
<emphasis box="[335,392,1735,1759]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">et al.</emphasis>
(2008)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated the need to remove the species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1810" box="[935,1065,1735,1759]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="candollei">
<emphasis box="[935,1065,1735,1759]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">L. candollei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the genus 
<emphasis box="[1248,1399,1735,1759]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gouan" authorityYear="1770" box="[1248,1395,1735,1759]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Lepadogaster</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Canestrini G." box="[242,429,1767,1791]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" pagination="177 - 196" refId="ref38859" refString="Canestrini G. 1864. Studi sui Lepadogaster del Mediterraneo. Archivio per la Zoologia, L'Anatomia e la Fisiologia 3: 177 - 196." type="journal article" year="1864">Canestrini (1864)</bibRefCitation>
had previously suggested placing 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1810" box="[794,921,1767,1791]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="candollei">
<emphasis box="[794,921,1767,1791]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">L. candollei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in a different genus (
<taxonomicName box="[1147,1240,1767,1791]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Mirbelia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Fabales" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1147,1240,1767,1791]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Mirbelia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), distinct from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gouan" authorityYear="1770" box="[242,389,1799,1823]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[242,389,1799,1823]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Lepadogaster</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In turn 
<bibRefCitation author="Briggs J. C." box="[482,634,1799,1823]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" pagination="33 - 39" refId="ref38833" refString="Briggs J. C. 1955. A Monograph of the Clingfish (Order Xenopterygii). Stanford Ichthyological Bulletin 6: 33 - 39." type="journal article" year="1955">Briggs (1955)</bibRefCitation>
, in his detailed revision, although placing 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1810" box="[1089,1216,1799,1823]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="candollei">
<emphasis box="[1089,1216,1799,1823]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">L. candollei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gouan" authorityYear="1770" box="[1252,1399,1799,1823]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1252,1399,1799,1823]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Lepadogaster</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
noted that: ‘‘ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Risso" authorityYear="1810" box="[385,515,1831,1855]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="candollei">
<emphasis box="[385,515,1831,1855]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">L. candollei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is well separated from the other three forms [of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gouan" authorityYear="1770" box="[1067,1214,1831,1855]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiesocidae" genus="Lepadogaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gobiesociformes" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1067,1214,1831,1855]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Lepadogaster</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] which are very closely related to each other”.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
